{
  "stem": "20609.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was-- was composed by a very famous composer in-- in Theresienstadt, which is now classic, which is now being-- a lot of kids are doing it, you know, like it's a children opera.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And a tremendous amount of talent because again, we had some of the greatest painters who got in trouble because they really painted all the-- the way it really was, besides what they did for the SS.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So-- but in 1944, like the end of 1944-- September, October-- all bets were off.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were no more prominent Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All-- all of a sudden, the prominent Jews we used to have in that orchard was gone.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Let me tell you what else we did in that orchard.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- there was-- there was like a-- like a little building there, like one of those garden buildings like-- I don't know, like an open-- gazebo, like a gazebo all broken down.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But underneath, we dug a big hole and we-- we put apples in there and pears in there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, we don't go there anymore and it-- it gets locked up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The place gets locked up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I pass it every time when I go outside the city with-- with the-- with the gendarmes, right?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So one day I had a good gendarme.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I says, I-- I think I left something over here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Can I jump over the fence and pick it up?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm only going to be two minutes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I think there's some apples in there, I'll bring you enough for yourself.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He said, OK, jump over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I jumped over the fence, I opened this thing up, and the smell was killing me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All-- turned-- all were rotten, you know, because we hadn't been there for two or three months, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
